Dialogs.Dialog: (What should I do？ Should I call out to her？)
Oh, so you heard me after all.
(Is it impossible for us to talk in a friendlier manner...？)
Well then, shall I go home？
You could at least greet me.
You could at least just leave me alone.
In a bad mood, huh？ What happened？
What...？ People were complaining about my attitude... Why can't they just come to borrow books with their mouths shut？
How could they borrow books if they don't say anything...？
(I shouldn't provoke her any more than this...)
(Um... What do I do with these...？)
Um, what do I do with these？
(As cold as always... But she taught me what to do, after all.)
(If I work on it, I could probably do something with it...)
No, I don't really have any business here...
(Eh？ Was that girl who just turned around the corner ▲小早川＊▲？)
No, no. You're not that small. I was just in a hurry, so...
That's right. You're very small, so I didn't see you.
What are you, a grade schooler？
So？ Going to the arcade again？
Well, I'll be off. Don't you have something to do too？
What are you, a grade schooler？
Well, something like that. See you.
(This time, it was ▲小早川＊▲ who called out to me...)
(Hmm. I wonder if this book belongs to this shelf...)
What are you, a grade schooler？
(Hasn't she become a bit kind lately？)
(Should I read a book here, or go home？)
(All right. I'll act like a library committee member and read a book for now.)
What are you, a grade schooler？
So what are you doing？ Reading？ Sleeping？
Sorry to bother you, but I'm going now, so please take care of locking the room.
(Huh, that's ▲小早川＊▲. Where is she going？)
What are you, a grade schooler？
Where are you going？ Class is starting.
(I gotta go to the staff room...)
What are you, a grade schooler？
Not really. I just happened to come this way.
(So she just used me to kill some time...？)
▲小早川＊▲. Do you need something from me？
Ah！ Sorry, I got carried away talking. Did you need something？
It's pretty easy to spot you from afar.
Ah！ Did I force you to stand here and accompany me for a while？
No. It's Rinko that was nice enough to accompany you.
▲小早川＊▲. What's wrong？ Why were you running？
Hehe, because I saw you here.
Okay. Sorry to keep you here.
No. It would be good if we could talk more.
All right. I should just put them in order, right？
Geez. Who left this stepladder here？ Must be some short person...
Ouch！ I'm helping you, aren't I？
You upset me, so you deserved it. But also, thanks for helping.
(The work today seems to be tough...)
Well, can we skip the work today and go to the arcade instead？
Hey, hey！ We got a lot to do. Skipping work will cause trouble for others.
Hmm. I didn't really mean that...
Phew. All done... By the way, the teacher called me earlier...
Then I'll have to go to the staff room now.
Oh, the bell's ringing. Go back to your class.
(Maybe I'll take a nap until my next class...)
(I need to go to the toilet...)
Why？ You were sleeping and didn't notice that Rinko was in the hallway！
If you have any business with me, just call me up.
Don't blame others when it's your fault！ Idiot！
▲小早川＊▲. Is there anything you want？
Is it okay for Rinko to stay in this classroom for the next class？
Hey, hey. Go back to your class.
Well, we're in a secluded area now.
Well, we're in a secluded area now.
Geez, that face... You're so crafty.
Well, we're in a secluded area now.
Fine. Only a little bit, okay？
Just so you know, this time is special... Okay？
I'm just thinking that it's very quiet here.
I'm just thinking that it's very quiet here.
You're making that face again... Ah！
I'm just thinking that it's very quiet here.
No one is watching us now.
No one is watching us now.
No one is watching us now.
